<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🎵 CTE Vibe Code - 智能 AI 開發平台</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding: 2rem 0; }
        .header h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .github-info {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header class="header">
            <h1>🎵 CTE Vibe Code</h1>
            <p>智能 AI 開發平台 - Over The Air 模型更新整合</p>
            
            <div class="github-info">
                <h3>📂 GitHub 倉庫</h3>
                <a href="https://github.com/Benisonpin/ai-agent-control-center.git" 
                   target="_blank" style="color: #60a5fa; text-decoration: none;">
                    https://github.com/Benisonpin/ai-agent-control-center.git
                </a>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                    ✅ SSH 連接已設定 | 🔄 自動同步 | 🚀 即時部署
                </p>
            </div>
        </header>
        
        <!-- 智能終端會在這裡自動插入 -->
    </div>
    
    <script src="js/smart-vibe-integration.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
